    "answer": "C",
    "solution": "$u=e^x-1$; $\\int\\frac{e^x\\cdot e^x}{e^x-1}dx=\\int\\frac{u+1}{u}du=u+\\ln|u|+C=e^x+\\ln(e^x-1)+C$"
